The paper focuses on 3D shape recognition using deep learning models, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of point cloud and multi-view data also suggests that the paper may be relevant to the graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the proposed embedding attention fusion scheme involves attention mechanisms, which are commonly used in natural language processing and may relate to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category.
